    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Removing your cloak and throwing it at an enemy as a thrown simple weapon with a range of 10 feet, the target creature, if hit, must save against @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.dN8QBNuTiaBHCKUe]{Baleful Polymorph} (using your casting DC or class DC, whichever is highest) attempting to turn them into your animal. If that animal would normally not be harmless, they become a young, harmless, version of that animal for the duration. The cloak is lost while they are transformed, and falls to the ground when they turn back. You may, as a manipulate action, remove the cloak from them, ending the effect, if they are within reach.</p>",
